{"tid":891784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得 舊式居屋完勝私樓","createTime":"2018-11-06T11:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T02:51:41.000Z","uid":151496,"like":28,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bff03f8206559be28f4965648c686746aaae856a","tid":891784,"uid":151496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"舊式居屋 雖然個價泊得住私樓<br />\n<br />\n計實用面積 完勝私樓，兩房一廳喺基本，廁所至少容納到2，3個人，廚房都叫大 <br />\n<br />\n無落地大玻璃，大打風都唔會爆<br />\n<br />\n居屋無豪華會所，管理費唔會過千 一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊式居屋 大多近地鐵站，有啲位處於山上，屬寧靜區域<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有 好多附近有 街市，體育館，圖書館<br />\n<br />\n舊式居屋，鄰居同鄰居都有善啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊式居屋唔好處，夠期驗樓，窗 麻煩啲，同埋唔少錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n私樓，細到連廚房都開放式，個廁所又細，大多落地大玻璃，打風都有機會爆 <br />\n<br />\n私樓超豪華會所，管理費過千 一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n私樓好多插針式 起喺旺區，舊區，夠矖嘈 <br />\n近海又濕氣勁"},{"pid":"d105175b8b115aac030310116a2367e8212fa4a4","tid":891784,"uid":117200,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"舊式=英治<br />\n新個堆=大陸風格"},{"pid":"c556715c9985a9c21236b462120dbe37baeab6f4","tid":891784,"uid":180373,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"居屋仔一世都唔明私樓好處"},{"pid":"7804021c629f375316e3d349689ab2d7441768b0","tid":891784,"uid":77222,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c556715c9985a9c21236b462120dbe37baeab6f4","tid":891784,"uid":180373,"like":10,"dislike":13,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"居屋仔一世都唔明私樓好處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"2種都有 點解會唔明"},{"pid":"d03cdbe03bfdc78291c322d41868885021aa8f2f","tid":891784,"uid":42509,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c556715c9985a9c21236b462120dbe37baeab6f4","tid":891784,"uid":180373,"like":10,"dislike":13,"